extendedInfo.description: If you are Future's fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check Future's lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all Future's lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of Future's lyrics are here. You can quickly search the lyrics by using the search bar at the top of the page.Hope you guy enjoy using this app as much as I enjoy developing it. :)-------------------------------- Main Features -------------------------------- - Lyrics categorized by album - Show all lyrics - Search lyrics-------------------------------- List of albums -------------------------------- - Pluto-------------------------------- List of lyrics -------------------------------- - Abu Intro Turn Up- Ain't No Way Around It- Astronaut Chick- Back At It- Ball Forever- Best 2 Shine- Bigger Picture- Billionaire Minds- Birds Take A Bath- Bitches Love Me- Blast Off- Blow- Ceelo- Chosen One- Deeper Than The Ocean- DNA- Easter Pink- Everything Ours- Finessin- First Class Flights- Fishscale- Fo Real- Freeband Gang- Future Back- Go Harder- Gone To The Moon- Homicide- I'm Trippin'- Intro- Itchin'- Jealous- Jordan Diddy- Jordan Diddy Interlude- Karate Chop- Keep On Shinin- Killin it- Long Live The Pimp- Long Time Coming- Magic- Magic (Remix)- Mark McGwire- Mind Blown- Muphucka- My- My Ho 2- My Name Hold Weight- Name Hold Weight- Neva End- Neva End (Remix)- Never Be The Same- Never Seen These- Never Seen Those Skit- No Matter What- Nunbout- OG D Drop- Parachute- Paradise- Permanent Scar- Pop Them Bands- Rider- Running Through A Check- Same Damn Time- Same Damn Time (Remix)- See It To Believe It- Shopping Spree- Smoke & Mirrors- Smoke And Mirrors- Space Cadets- Spaz On Yall- Straight Up- Swap It Out- The Future Is Now- Tony Montana- Trance- Truth Gonna Hurt You- Turn On The Lights- Turn On The Lights (Remix)- Unconditional Love- Watch This- Whats Wrong- Whip Game- You Deserve It- You Wonder- YSL Cheetah
